; Items in boxes
; def_box 					- only roubles can drop out of it (10% chance)
; med_box_low				- basic drugs
; med_box_advanced			- basic + advanced drugs
; med_box_high				- high tier + basic + advanced drugs
; small_box_generic 		- any ammo except big explosives
; small_box_full			- roubles + any items except big ones, no ammo
; small_box_ussr 			- roubles + walkie + any ammo except big explosives and gauss ammo
; small_box_nato 			- roubles + walkie + any ammo except big explosives and gauss ammo
; small_box_army 			- roubles + walkie + any ammo except big explosives
; small_box_science 		- high tier + basic + advanced drugs
; big_box_generic 			- any items + the big ones + big ammo
; big_box_dungeons 			- any items + the big ones + more chance for big ammo + big explosives + gauss ammo
; big_box_arsenal 			- any items + the big ones + more chance for big ammo + more chance for big explosives and gauss ammo


